---
title: Bone-In Pork Chops with Roasted Pear, Collards, and Shallot Cream Sauce
description: Bone-in pork chops make for a dramatic presentation—and stay extra juicy to boot! Of course, it doesn’t hurt to smother them in a delicious, creamy sauce. Roasting pears in the oven sweetens and intensifies their flavor—you’ll fall in love with this technique!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/56abc0614dab7180108b4567.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/56abc0614dab7180108b4567.pdf
